    rating: "TODO"
    comments: "The direction on a macroscale is unique and interesting as they basically had a narratively driven documentary about Pharrell's life but told it through Legos, and used the Lego animation well to help paint the world and show Pharrell's imagination; the direction on a microscale feels like an interview-style docuemntary, though Pharrell is given space to work with and share his emotions; the storytelling is very similiar to other docuemntaries, though told in a very meta, creative style"
